  "title": "Retail Assistants & Supervisors (Sports, Mobile, Eyewear, Beauty, Fashion)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Summary</strong></h2><ul><li>Various Industries: Eyewear / Beauty / Mobile / Home Appliances / Clothing / Footwear, etc.</li><li>Across Island wide Locations</li><li>Basic Salary + Commission + OT </li></ul><p></p><h2><strong>Job </strong>Responsibilities<strong>:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Assist customers and provide product information</p></li><li><p>Promote products and explain offers or promotions</p></li><li><p>Arrange and replenish products on display</p></li><li><p>Handle basic cashier or sales transactions</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and neatness of the store</p></li><li><p>Achieve sales targets and provide good customer service<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><h2><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Prior retail sales experience is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Friendly, outgoing, and customer-oriented personality</p></li><li><p>Willing to work retail shifts, including weekends and public holidays<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p>To Apply, kindly click on the <strong>\"APPLY NOW\"</strong> button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><strong>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Yuphine Lee | R22108749</strong></p>",
